Frist of all we need download OpenSSH Client this program give access to remote machines ,in WindowsPowerShell To view the syntax of the ssh command,run : "ssh"If you see an error message saying the command isn’t found, you will need to sign out and sign in again. Rebooting your PC will also work.
For example, to connect to an SSH server at ssh.example.com with the username “bob”, you’d run:
ssh bob@ssh.example.com
TROUBLESHOOTING SSH CONNECTIONS: 
1. Ping your VPS
Ping is Successful Now What?
2. Use VNC to gain access if internet connection is established but SSH is not.
3. Verify the VPS Firewall Rules
4. Verify the SSH Service Status
5. Verify the SSH Port
